Behavioral Questions:
Question 1: Why Did You Leave Your Last Job? 

situation:I have been working for them for four years. It was time for a challenge!

Task: I was the only driver for them delivering lumber. With little to no room to grow!


Action: Signed up for night courses at Codefellows, moved close to work so I could work full time and go to school! 


Result: Over the last year I finished school, learned Javascript all while working full time!


